src:
LIVE: Proleter – Crvena zvezda
02 Nov 2019, 15:58 by Darko
Naši čitaoci mogu da prate direktan prenos utakmice 15. kola Linglong Super lige Srbije između Proletera i Crvene zvezde.
Članovi mogu da prate prenos u HQ 800×600 formatu, bez reklama i prekida klikom na link SCTV Live! u gornjem desnom uglu ove stranice.
Ostali čitaoci prenos mogu da prate u boksu ispod.




POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
LIVE: Proleter - Red Star
02 Nov 2019, 14:58 by Darko
Our readers can follow the live broadcast of the 15th round of the Linglong Super League of Serbia between Proleter and Red Star.
Members can watch the download in HQ 800 × 600 format, without ads and interruptions by clicking the SCTV Live link! at the top right of this page.
Other readers of the broadcast can follow in the box below.
